OL,3,CSwitzerland and Italy to redraw part
OL,4,Cof their border due to melting glaciers
OL,6,FPart of the border between Italy and
OL,7,FSwitzerland is set to be redrawn as
OL,8,Fthe glaciers that mark the boundary
OL,9,Fmelt, in yet another sign of how much
OL,10,Fhumans are changing the world by
OL,11,Fburning planet-heating fossil fuels.
OL,13,FThe two countries have agreed to
OL,14,Fchange the border under the iconic
OL,15,FMatterhorn Peak, one of the highest
OL,16,Fsummits in the Alps, which overlooks
OL,17,FZermatt, a popular skiing destination.
