OL,3,CSwitzerland and Italy to redraw part
OL,4,Cof their border due to melting glaciers
OL,6,FWhile national boundaries are often
OL,7,Fthought of as fixed, large sections of
OL,8,Fthe Swiss-Italian border are defined
OL,9,Fby glaciers and snow fields.
OL,11,F"With the melting of the glaciers,
OL,12,Fthese natural elements evolve and
OL,13,Fredefine the national border," the
OL,14,FSwiss government said in a statement
OL,15,Fon Friday.
OL,17,FThe border changes were agreed back in
OL,18,F2023 and the Swiss government
OL,19,Fofficially approved the adjustment on
OL,20,FFriday. The process for approval is
OL,21,Funderway in Italy.
