OL,6,FAs soon as both parties have signed,
OL,7,Fthe agreement will be published and
OL,8,Fdetails of the new border made public,
OL,9,Faccording to the Swiss government.
OL,11,FEurope is the world's fastest-warming
OL,12,Fcontinent and the impact on its
OL,13,Fglaciers has been stark.
OL,15,FIn Switzerland, they are melting at an
OL,16,Falarming rate. The country's glaciers
OL,17,Flost 4% of their volume last year,
OL,18,Fsecond only to the record-setting 6%
OL,19,Flost in 2022.
