OL,3,CSwitzerland and Italy to redraw part
OL,4,Cof their border due to melting glaciers
OL,6,FThis downward trend shows no sign of
OL,7,Fending, said Matthias Huss, a
OL,8,Fglaciologist at the Swiss university
OL,9,FETH Zurich and director of GLAMOS, the
OL,10,FSwiss glacier monitoring network.
OL,12,F"In 2024, glaciers continued to lose
OL,13,Fice at a high speed despite much snow
OL,14,Fin winter that was expected to bring
OL,15,Fsome relief," he told CNN. "Some
OL,16,Fglaciers are literally falling apart,
OL,17,Fsmall glaciers are disappearing."
