OL,11,FEven with the most ambitious climate
OL,12,Faction, up to half the world's
OL,13,Fglaciers may be gone by 2100. It's
OL,14,Fcausing a cascade of impacts.
OL,16,FIt makes the landscape more unstable,
OL,17,Fand prone to dangerous landslides and
OL,18,Fcollapses. In 2022, 11 people died
OL,19,Fwhen a glacier collapsed in the
OL,20,FItalian Alps.
