OL,3,CSwitzerland and Italy to redraw part
OL,4,Cof their border due to melting glaciers
OL,6,FShrinking glaciers are leading to grim
OL,7,Fdiscoveries. Last year, the remains of
OL,8,Fa mountain climber who had gone
OL,9,Fmissing 37 years earlier while hiking
OL,10,Fnear the Matterhorn were recovered.
OL,12,FAs they recede, glaciers are also
OL,13,Flosing their vital role in
OL,14,Fcontributing to freshwater, which
OL,15,Fcould aggravate shortages during heat
OL,16,Fwaves.
