OL,6,FThe shift of national borders "is one
OL,7,Fsmall side-effect" of glaciers
OL,8,Fmelting, Huss said. But when people
OL,9,Fcan see it "directly affects our world
OL,10,Fmap," he added, it makes the immense
OL,11,Fchanges of a warming world much more
OL,12,Fvisible.
